{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)PushwooshConfig(cm)setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets additional notification authorization options beyond the SDK defaults.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"UNAuthorizationOptions","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@UNAuthorizationOptions"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"options"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The additional "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptions"},{"text":" to request.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"options"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"registerForPushNotifications","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the SDK requests these permissions by default:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptionBadge"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptionSound"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptionAlert"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNAuthorizationOptionCarPlay","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to request additional capabilities on top of the defaults.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The options you set here are combined (bitwise OR) with the default options"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"before being passed to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenter.requestAuthorizationWithOptions:"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be called "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"before","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"registerForPushNotifications"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Available-Options","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Available Options"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNAuthorizationOptionProvisional","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (iOS 12+) — Delivers notifications quietly to the Notification Center","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"without showing a permission dialog. The user sees notifications silently and can then choose to keep or disable them."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this for a “soft opt-in” strategy to avoid users declining the permission prompt upfront.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptionCriticalAlert"},{"type":"text","text":" (iOS 12+) — Allows notifications that bypass Do Not Disturb and the mute switch."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Requires a special entitlement from Apple (must be approved via Apple Developer portal).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Intended for medical, health, safety, and public security apps."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNAuthorizationOptionProvidesAppNotificationSettings","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (iOS 12+) — Adds a “Configure in App” button"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the system notification settings for your app. When tapped, iOS calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"userNotificationCenter:openSettingsForNotification:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on your "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig\/addNotificationCenterDelegate:","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" to register your delegate and handle this callback."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptionAnnouncement"},{"text":" (iOS 13+) — Allows Siri to automatically read out notifications","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"through AirPods and compatible headphones."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example-Provisional-Soft-Opt-In","text":"Example — Provisional (Soft Opt-In)","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","","    if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.provisional])","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","    return true","}"]},{"text":"Example — In-App Notification Settings Button","anchor":"Example-In-App-Notification-Settings-Button","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","","    if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.providesAppNotificationSettings])","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.addNotificationCenterDelegate(self)","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","    return true","}","","\/\/ Called when user taps \"Configure in App\" in system notification settings","func userNotificationCenter(_ center: UNUserNotificationCenter,","                            openSettingsFor notification: UNNotification?) {","    \/\/ Navigate to your in-app notification settings screen","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example-Combining-Multiple-Options","text":"Example — Combining Multiple Options"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["if #available(iOS 12.0, *) {","    Pushwoosh.configure.setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions([.provisional, .providesAppNotificationSettings])","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Objective-C:"}]},{"syntax":"objc","type":"codeListing","code":["if (@available(iOS 12.0, *)) {","    [Pushwoosh.configure setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:UNAuthorizationOptionProvisional | UNAuthorizationOptionProvidesAppNotificationSettings];","}","","[Pushwoosh.configure registerForPushNotifications];"]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pushwooshconfig\/setadditionalauthorizationoptions:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig\/setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PushwooshConfig":{"title":"PushwooshConfig",